    "2myi": {
      "id": "2myi",
      "title": "Add intake command",
      "body": "\n## Log\n- 2026-02-19: Implemented intake command with file/STDIN reading, opencode integration, tests, and documentation\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n1. **CLI Interface**\n   - [x] Add `intake` command to CLI with optional file path argument\n   - [x] Support reading from STDIN when no file is provided\n   - [x] Support reading from file when path is provided\n\n2. **Text Processing**\n   - [x] Read content from file or STDIN\n   - [x] Parse text to identify a single top-level issue\n   - [x] Identify all child issues from the text\n   - [x] Pass structured data to opencode with instructions to create issues\n\n3. **Issue Creation**\n   - [x] Launch opencode with `/intake` command\n   - [x] Create a single parent/top-level change\n   - [x] Create all other changes as children of the parent change\n   - [x] Each change should have a title extracted from the text\n\n4. **Error Handling**\n   - [x] Handle file not found errors gracefully\n   - [x] Handle empty input gracefully\n   - [x] Validate pebbles repository is initialized\n",
      "status": "done",
      "priority": "medium",
      "changelog_type": "feature",
      "parent": null,
